              You can pick any integers you want for <m>a</m> and <m>b</m>.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              Hint: You need to check that <m>I</m> and <m>U</m> satisfy the implicit condition that defines <m>\mathscr{E}</m>.
            </p>
